TITLE="DevOps Trainee Needed for Our Team"
MSG="""I will like to inform you that we are seeking a DevOps person to join our team as a trainee for the purpose of gaining work experience. <br /><br />
The DevOps trainee will be responsible for building and maintaining our application deployment process. The trainee will need to interface with web developers and 1 Linux administrator. <br /><br />
As a trainee, the DevOps person will be assigned a mentor to guide him/her in this program <br /><br />
Our company will maintain a work history porfolio for the DevOps trainee to help convince prospective employers that he/she has completed these tasks and is competent in the field.<br /><br />
If you or someone you know is interested in adding DevOps skills to his/her/your linux skills, please send me the resume, title: Interested in DevOps. <br /><br />
This will be your opportunity to do hands-on work and you will using Jenkins, Docker, Puppet, Git, and Maven. The cost is $399 and the training will be for 3 months. <br /><br />
"""

